    "To detect these items independent of the capturing tools, the Metaverse's object detector needs to be strengthened.",
    "Issues with data and class distribution make up the second.",
    "In the Metaverse, it is often simple to gather large datasets with more than 100 classes, but it is more difficult to gather datasets with a diverse scene and class distribution.",
    "The final one is the Metaverse's object detection computational burden.",
    "The Metaverse's 3D immersive universe has a variety of information that must be distributed even in remote areas."
